 With 400 shortlisted entrants so far, the next three weeks will determine the remaining 600 babies who will progress to the next stage of the Cussons Baby Moments 6 competition. Remember, you have the opportunity of entering the competition multiple times if your baby did not make the shortlist in the first two weeks. Just take a better, more creative picture of your baby and enter again to stand a better chance of being shortlisted this week. To enter for the Cussons Baby Moments 6 competition, you only have to do the following: The competition is only open to babies within the ages of 0 – 24 months and entries close on October 18th, 2019. Entrants are advised to familiarize themselves with the terms and conditions of this competition. It is available on the website entry page. Cussons Baby will also be at the Ikeja City Mall in Lagos this Saturday, October 5th, 2019, so be on the lookout for them as there will be loads of fun-family games and prizes to be won, and also you can take creative photos of your baby and enter for the competition right there at the venue. To keep up with the competition, kindly follow @cussonsbabyng on Instagram and Twitter, and Facebook, or use the hashtags #SharingMagicMemories and #CBM6. —————————————————————————————————————————————– Sponsored Content The post The race to make the Top 1000 is heating up as Cussons Baby Moments 6 reaches its 3rd Week of Entries – Enter Now! appeared first on BellaNaija – Showcasing Africa to the world. Read today!. Source: Bella Naija